<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_521" id="260r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_521_r1l5">Hanſen von Maẏental </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l6"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vogt cʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Ergl </del> <expan>Erlang<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_521_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / vvie daʒ vvir nach ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l8">vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knehten ſtellen / vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf ew halten laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l9">dauon vviſʒen wir niht / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l10">daʒ ſie auf ew 
<del rend="strikethrough">beſunder </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_521_line_1576348522219_3617">beſunder </ab></add> halten ſüllen / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ſchicken vnder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l11">vveẏlen 
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener auſʒ vnd heıſſen die halten / ob <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l12">die <expan>ſtraſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> angriffe vnd rawbet / daʒ ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dauor vveren vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l13">werten <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ſie möchten / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_521" id="260r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen von Mayental <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> vogt czu
                        <expan>Erlang<ex>en</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie daz wir nach
                        ew und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knehten stellen und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf ew halten lassen, davon wiszen
                        wir niht und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
                        daz sie auf ew <add>besunder</add> halten süllen;
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir schicken under weylen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener ausz und heissen die halten, ob
                                <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> die
                            <expan>strasze<ex>n</ex></expan> angriffe und rawbet, daz sie
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> davor weren und das werten,
                                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> sie möchten.</ab>
</div>
